					<description><![CDATA[不知道大家有没有这样一种体会，有时候拿到一种水果不知道怎么剥，比如石榴，芒果什么的！现在就教大家切水果的好方法 [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">不知道大家有没有这样一种体会，有时候拿到一种水果不知道怎么剥，比如石榴，芒果什么的！现在就教大家切水果的好方法。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">1.不用剥皮就可以吃到蜜柑</strong></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/a7808445972689aa894b2b5a6da9f65b.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">蜜柑去头去尾(千万不要切太过，不然会把果肉切走变得不好看，一般蜜柑的皮都不会太厚)，然后在果皮上纵向切断果皮，最后慢慢拉扯开果肉，让它们展开即可。</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/b49d646d3f6639552a0124609a9491ab.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">2.最干净方便的吃西瓜方法</strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">step 1: 西瓜对半切开</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/f9ca84dd87e8c0360bf030a3d56c55ce.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/8e41f523b08f6fcde9df0100b1eab41f.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">step 2: 将西瓜橫切面朝下放，然后纵向切段，距离约1英寸</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/a48f6393aa0c6678fa78d63653084f1f.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">step 3: 再以同样的距离橫向切段，然后就有不会吃得滿脸都是，也不用怕果汁到处滴的西瓜棒享用啦~</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/6bb40f82af57f73c974706692596db1c.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">3.轻松取石榴果肉粒的诀窍</strong></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/e5afee3e06835536fcbc3e532aacce08.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">step 1: 石榴对半切，在干净碗內裝适量饮用水</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/54512cf1fdc7a69e4aca22a16e431c3f.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">step 2: 一手拿着切开的半个石榴，橫切面朝著裝了水的容器</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/3379d3ccb39ed870c9147e786dcd767f.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">step 3: 用勺子用力拍打石榴，让果肉掉进水里.</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/10754c75712499ea1952f57425997990.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">step 4: 捞起漂浮在水上的薄皮即可大口享用，无需再边吃边拨那麼麻烦</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/b538dd9815915158e08208b12e7999bd.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">4.奇异果如何去皮</strong></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/506dd82c81aa1981c6babe94a667ba23.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">step 1:奇异果切头切尾</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/a17a3946814e46fcc61331277e9bb76d.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">step2：勺子插入奇异果，尽可能貼著果皮，然后旋转起肉即可。虽然奇异果对半切开再用勺子挖來吃也很方便，但如果是想用來做餐点装饰，这样起肉再切片的效果会最美观哦!(tips：勺子要接近奇异果的大小)</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">5.如何切出沒有果衣的漂亮柑橘类水果</strong></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/dd9d4242d19eed0762efc3187865cce5.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">step 1 : 水果切头切尾(有的柑橘类水果的果皮会比较厚，所以要根据实际情況來切，标准是切到看不到果皮)</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/7bd07bb90256e7aef1e8027d99bc786a.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">step 2 : 选一個切面朝下，竖着切掉果皮</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/a95a13aa6cd38a4739a266f9f84d66d0.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">step 3 : 根据果衣的间距來切出成瓣的果肉(这一步最好在碗上進行，切好后可以直接掉入碗內，还可以保存滴下的果汁)</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/b67ce76a427c549885d722f8bc2c536e.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">6. 如何快速起出菠萝(凤梨)肉</strong></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/025cbf143cc994f44a05d79810a2c5f3.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">step 1: 菠萝(凤梨)去头去尾，立在砧板上，然后打竖对半切开</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/bdcb4717e286695825d5cc13fbb9b145.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">step 2: 果肉再对半切开，然后把芯切掉</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/c4e7ebcf2d6630d4e3f68cc1ead692f7.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">step 3: 最後把果肉段切块即可</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">7.最彻底最完美的桃子去皮方法</strong></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/3c5b44662225a290a40ee9a5f16b1f9c.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">step 1: 先准备好一盆冰水和一锅沸水</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/1a6e1ec87802fe1051bd433b6e179232.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">step 2: 桃子末端用刀划十字</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/3b5fe1b20a63ad761b321e6a2c7dfe75.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">step 3: 把桃子放进沸水里煮大約35-45秒(要整個桃子都浸入沸水里头哦~</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">step 4：用漏勺捞出，然后立刻放入冰水中</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/d9d57c398a5e1a06907ab81b3aac7a85.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/1173d9739a6cd896bb26fb1b4252250b.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">step 5: 用手撕掉果皮即可</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">这個方法虽然不是最快的，但绝对最彻底好美观哦!</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/176b86eb1e63bfb36d93f3a483aa733b.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">8. 如何完美起出牛油果(酪梨)肉 (1)</strong></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/9edd34fd24a5779969e923d531142bef.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">step 1: 牛油果(酪梨)握在手里，用刀沿著牛油果外围划一圈</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/668276e88df3023de67041426e39cd3a.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">step 2: 用刀划完一圈之后，双手握住牛油果扭一扭然后掰开兩半</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/c2743b3f197fa22cacc6b7e9600ccc0e.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">step 3: 用一把锋利一点的刀插入牛油果核，卡住後轻轻把核拔出</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/70af15951c3b6c6837bb0012b272e349.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">step 4：在去核的牛油果上纵橫切段</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/d7312cf4f397ec817b5da3ba5a97ec98.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">step 5：最后用勺子起出即可</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">　　<strong style="color: blue;">9. 如何完美起出牛油果肉 (2)</strong></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/c48ffc6cfb4b112d55ffa7df9e0639ae.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">step 1：依照刚刚的方法去核，然后把果肉一开四(只需把果肉划开即可，不需要把皮也切断)</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2ddf5d2223287bb8e1b2e424d59dddd8.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">step 2: 像吃橙子一样的手勢轻轻地把皮剥掉就可以了</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/5119bd97ee945d9fdd3f38a3cdc5d7f9.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">当然啦，你也可以在去核之後直接用勺子挖出整个果肉，然后再切片~</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/f3ca159432f67b4728e32bc0233b0489.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>


</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
